<section id="historique" class="historique">
    <div class="container section-title">
        <p>
            Passed on from father to son, three passionate generations have each in turn committed themselves to satisfying their customers by offering top-of-the-line service and excellent work at all times with assistance from a team that shares their same values.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container historique-body">
        <div id="historiquebody" class="">
            <div class="timeline-border">
